sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as Client App
    participant WESTON as Compositor (Weston)
    participant DRM as DRM/KMS
    participant DISP as Display
    APP->>APP: Render to buffer
    APP->>WESTON: wl_surface.attach(buffer)
    APP->>WESTON: wl_surface.commit()
    WESTON->>WESTON: Compose all surfaces
    WESTON->>DRM: Atomic commit
    DRM->>DISP: Page flip
    DISP-->>WESTON: VSync
    WESTON-->>APP: frame callback
    Note over WESTON,DRM: 60 FPS = 16.67ms per frame<br/>Receive buffers<br/>Compose<br/>Submit to DRM
